data.description: Where Country &City life collide. This 3BR/2BA  Beautiful Brick Home, with a sparkling in-ground pool, is nestled on a 1.2 acre lot. It is half mile to the new Publix Shopping Center& New Medical Center.Beyond the blueberry orchard, are  fig,plum,&apple trees.This home so many recent upgrades to include: Newly painted inside & outside,new blinds,new SS appliances,new custom cabinets & counter tops,recently remodeled BA rooms,new lighting inside & outside,new ceiling fans,new fencing around the pool& blueberries,new pool robot which conveys & new gas logs in the FP & more! The  50 galH2O heater installed 2018 , HVAC installed 2020 & a new roof is ordered and will be installed prior to closing. If you are looking for your private Oasis, in the city, look no further, It's right here!
